name: Antonov Airlines An-124 "Ruslan" [UR-82007] Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
The Ruslan returns! It's always a pleasure to see one of these massive Ukrainian aircraft in Calgary, especially up close like this. Here we have UR-82007, one of 7 An-124s in Antonov Airlines' fleet landing on runway 35R at a very hazy Calgary International Airport. ATC is included, hope you enjoy! 

Thanks for watching!
